    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >父亲和母亲去北京的女儿家中拜访，关于父亲对生活的认知，还有过去与母亲的回忆。</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3294060/extras/0cd553b622faca17c62cdeb869e531be.poster.avif?t=1760662120\" width=782 height=540 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3294060/extras/0cd553b622faca17c62cdeb869e531be.webm?t=1760662120\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3294060/extras/0cd553b622faca17c62cdeb869e531be.mp4?t=1760662120\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本游戏是<strong>免费独立短篇叙事</strong>游戏。我们希望通过简洁而深刻的剧情，为玩家带来一次独特的沉浸式体验。虽然游戏时间不长，但我们在每一个细节上都倾注了心血。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >感谢您花时间进入我们的世界，愿您的旅程能够引起您的一些许感动和思考。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏QQ交流群：235579672；欢迎添加愿望单哦。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>故事梗概</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >父亲退休了，一直和母亲生活在一起的的父亲终于闲暇下来。想到不如去找远在外地的儿女，刚好他们又搬家回到了北京。母亲却不愿离开这个乡下小镇 ，女儿劝说下母亲终于动身。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >「父亲母亲去北京的女儿家中拜访，关于父亲对自己的归属认知，还有和过去和妻子的回忆」</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >过去回忆中的家人们虽然隔着遥远的距离，但是在相隔的电话两段却感受温暖</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >但来到北京的二人却感受到那遥远的村庄</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3294060/extras/f4d2bc8316389f044f421ed96e336764.poster.avif?t=1760662120\" width=540 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3294060/extras/f4d2bc8316389f044f421ed96e336764.webm?t=1760662120\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3294060/extras/f4d2bc8316389f044f421ed96e336764.mp4?t=1760662120\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>游戏特点</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >九十年代文学的故事风格</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在对话与探索中推进剧情</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >精美的手绘美术风格</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >令人震撼的精美手书</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >余音绕梁的优美配乐</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>操作方式</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >WASD：移动角色</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enter：确认/选择</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >F5：刷新游戏</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >F4：全屏游戏</p>",
